import { Grid, Paper } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

function DashboardMain() {
    return (
        <>
            <Paper>
                <Grid container spacing={3}>
                    <Grid item xs={3}>
                        First item
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={3}>
                        second
                    </Grid> 
                    <Grid item xs={3}>
                        third
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item xs={3}>
                        fourth
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </Paper>
        </>
    )
}

export default DashboardMain
